data.name: ReadProfile
data.value: select top(1) T1.NAME from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T3 join CKT_PROFILE T1 join CKT_SERV_PROV_PRO T2 on (T1.NAME = T2.PRO_NAME) and (T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) on (T3.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T2.SPD_GEN_ID) and (T3.USER_ID = @userId)
